=======================================
SBNET
=======================================
This is a startup project using the 
Zend Framework with custom settings and
configuration for rapid application 
development.

=======================================
Features
=======================================
* Service layer
* Custom ORM
* Caching
* Multi-language
* Logging
* UnitTest
* API documentation
* Pagination
* Navigation
* Search Lucene Index
* Acl

=======================================
Requirements
=======================================
* Zend Framework
* Phing
* unix based operating system
* PHPUnit
* PHPDocumentor
* PHP 5.3 or higher

=======================================
Build
=======================================
* Add your Db settings in the
  build.properties file
* Run the build.xml file with phing

